description:
It was a time when pirates ruled the seas. Several bands of pirates were battling over the great hidden treasure, One Piece, which was left by the now legendary pirate captain, Gold Roger. There was a young boy who admired the pirates, his name was http://anidb.net/ch474 [Monkey D. Luffy]. One day, he mistakenly eats the devil`s fruit and turns himself into a rubber human being.
Ten years have passed since that incident. Luffy sets out to sail all alone. He sets out to become a great pirate captain and that`s when his great adventure begins. "I`m going to be the Pirate King! I`m going to get One Piece!".

REGULAR.description:

Otama has been kidnapped by the Gifters! She is taken to a flourishing town called Bakura Town where a creepy-looking Headliner was expecting her. Luffy and Zoro rush to rescue her along with a samurai, Okiku!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Charging into the Enemy`s Territory! Bakura Town: Where Officials Thrive!
Perce en territoire ennemi. Bakura, la ville des administrateurs !
Tekijin Totsunyuu: Yakunin Habikoru Bakura-chou!
Vorsto in feindliches Gebiet!  Bakura, die Stadt der Beamten!

REGULAR.description:
As Luffy, Zoro, and Okiku bounce through Bakura Town on Komachiyos back, looking for the kidnapped Otama, a sumo wrestler comes flying towards them! Interested, they go down to watch sumo but the undefeated yokozuna Urashima has been expecting Okiku there and shows his brutal nature!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Auftritt des Yokozuna  Die Jagd des unbesiegbaren Urashima auf O-Kiku!
L`offensive du yokozuna. Urashima et O-Kiku !
The Yokozuna Appears! The Invincible Urashima Goes After Okiku!
Yokozuna Toujou: Okiku Nerau Muteki no Urashima!

REGULAR.description:
Luffy challenges Urashima, the strongest yokozuna in the Land of Wano, to a sumo match! Urashima even uses illegal moves to beat Luffy at any cost! Meanwhile, Holdem tells Otama that he knows she committed a crime and he has to punish her for it.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Climactic Sumo Battle! Straw Hat vs. the Strongest Ever Yokozuna!
Combat de sumo. Luffy affronte le yokozuna !
Ein gnadenloser Sumo-Wettkampf!  Der Strohhut gegen den strksten Yokozuna!
Sumou Kessen: Mugiwara vs Saikyou no Yokozuna!
VS!

REGULAR.description:
After sending the yokozuna Urashima flying, Luffy and his clan continue their search for Bakura Towns boss to save Otama! They finally find the boss, Holdem, one of the Beast Pirates Headliners, and Otama who is hanging in the mouth of a lion in Holdems stomach.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: La colre de Luffy.  la rescousse d`O-Tama !
Luffy Gekido: Pinch no Otama o Sukue!
Luffy Rages! Rescue Otama from Danger!
Ruffys Zorn!  Rettet O-Tama!

REGULAR.description:
Facing Holdem who is holding Otama as hostage, Luffy prepares for a fight but Okiku tries to stop him by sharing who is really ruling the region. Meanwhile, Basil Hawkins who is also working for Kaido and chasing after Luffy, is confronted by a mysterious figure.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Il faut librer O-Tama. L`affrontement contre Holdem !
Otama Dakkan: Gekitou! Holdem Sen!
Rettet O-Tama!  Ein erbitterter Kampf gegen Holdem!
Taking Back Otama! A Fierce Fight Against Holdem!

REGULAR.description:
Taking down Holdem, Luffy rescues Otama and tries to catch up to Zoro and Okiku who stole the food treasure ship and started a mad dash to get out of the town! Meanwhile, Trafalgar Laws attempt to silence Basil Hawkins fails when he hears bad news about his alliance.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Duel! The Magician and the Surgeon of Death!
Duell!  Der Magier und der Chirurg des Todes!
Ikkiuchi: Majutsushi to Shi no Gekai!
Le duel. Magicien et le chirurgien de la mort !

REGULAR.description:
This is a story of Luffy in an alternate reality. While sailing on the sea by himself, a strange bird crashes into his small boat. He looks up to find a giant ship where a girl named Ann has been captured. It seems like the bird belongs to her.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: 20 Shuunen Tokubetsu Hen "Romance Dawn"
20ROMANCE DAWN
Romance Dawn
Romance Dawn!
pisode spcial 20 ans. Romance Dawn !
One Piece! Romance Dawn

REGULAR.description:
Zoro and the others dash out of BakuraTown on the treasure ship filled with food! Luffy catches up to them bringing ahuge bucket of fresh water! Then, they distribute the food and the water to thepeople of Okobore Town who were thirsty and hungry.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Die Ankunft des Essensschiffes!  Ruffytaro revanchiert sich!
Le char de vivres. Luffytaro s`acquitte de ses dettes !
Takarabune Tourai: Luffytarou no Ongaeshi!
The Coming of the Treasure Ship! Luffytaro Returns the Favor!

REGULAR.description:
Luffy arrives at the ruins of Oden Castle following Law and finds the graves of his friends, Kinemon and the others. As Law starts telling the already-stunned Luffy about the creepy story of Kinemons ghost, Luffy sees it coming towards him!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Mysterious Grave Markers! A Reunion at the Ruins of Oden Castle!
Mysterise Grabsteine!  Wiedervereinigung in den Ruinen von Schloss Oden!
Mystrieuses pierres tombales. Retrouvailles au chteau !
Nazo no Bohyou: Oden Jou Ato de no Saikai!

REGULAR.description:
Kinemon tells Luffy and the others about how Kozuki Oden made Kuri into a peaceful region and became its Daimyo. However, he was set up by Kaido and Kurozumi Orochi and executed. Kinemon and his fellow vassals ran to Oden Castle in flames to save Odens wife Toki and children but Toki told him a shocking truth.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Legendary Samurai! The Man Who Roger Admired!
Densetsu no Samurai: Roger ga Horeta Otoko!
Ein legendrer Samurai!  Der Mann, den Roger bewunderte!
Le samoura lgendaire. L`homme qui charma mme Roger !

REGULAR.description:
Kinemon and the others crossed through time by the power of Kozuki Toki, Momonosukes mother, and arrived at the Land of Wano 20 years later, a totally different country before their eyes. However, discovering that there were still their allies there, they started preparing to take down Kaido and Orochi who ruined the country.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Bringing Down the Emperor of the Sea! A Secret Raid Operation Begins!
Datou Yonkou: Gokuhi Uchiiri Sakusen Hatsudou
Dtrner l`empereur. Une opration secrte est lance !
Sturz eines Kaisers der Meere! Die geheime berfalloperation beginnt!

REGULAR.description:
Ashura Doji, one of the allies Kinemon wants to search for, has become the head of a thieves brigade and they now raid Okobore Town taking away the food that Luffy gave to the people. Ashura Doji, under the name Shutenmaru, then faces Kaidos right-hand man and gets into a fierce fight!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Der strkste Mann! Shutenmaru der Anfhrer der Diebesbande!
Le plus puissant des hommes. Le chef des brigands, Shutenmaru !
Saikyou no Otoko: Touzokudan Touryou Shutenmaru!
The Strongest Man in the World! Shutenmaru, the Thieves Brigade Chief!

REGULAR.description:
The drunken Kaido flies above Okobore Town in his dragon form and threatens Shutenmaru and all the people in the town. Luffy, Law, Kinemon, and Okiku start running towards the town to rescue them. However, Kaido heads towards the ruins of Oden Castle where they left their crew behind.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Auf einen Schlag! Kaidos lodernder Flammen-Atem!
Everyone Is Annihilated! Kaido`s Furious Blast Breath!
L`quipage dcim. Le souffle ardent de Kaido !
Zen`in Shoumetsu: Kaidou Ikari no Boro Breath!

REGULAR.description:
After Luffy sees Kaido shattering the ruins of Oden Castle where he left his friends, he becomes enraged and attacks Kaido! Soon after, he finds out Kaido even assaulted Otama who was riding on Speeds back to her home. Furious, Luffy reveals himself to Kaido and starts to retaliate!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Ein gnadenloser Kampf! Ruffy gegen Kaido!
Enfin, la rencontre. Luffy, enrag, dfie Kaido !
Finally Clashing! The Ferocious Luffy vs. Kaido!
Tsui ni Gekitotsu: Moukou Luffy vs Kaidou
VS

REGULAR.description:
An infuriated Luffy strikes blow after blow on the drunken Kaido. When he activates Gear Four Bounce-Man and launches even more powerful attacks, Kaido fights back and knocks him out with just one blow. Law tries to rescue Luffy but is interrupted by Hawkins and now Kaido approaches Luffy, unconscious on the ground.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Destructive! One Shot, One Kill: Thunder Bagua!
Dvastation. Le Grondement du tonnerre divin !
Hakaiteki! Ichigeki Hissatsu no Raimei Hakke!
berwltigende Macht! Der vernichtende Bagua-Donnerschlag!

REGULAR.description:
Luffy gets beaten by Kaido and is sent to a great mine where prisoners are made to work in forced labor. There, he finds an unexpected reunion. Meanwhile, Okiku is rushing to the ruins of Oden Castle in order to confirm the safety of the Straw Hats and the others.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Living Hell! Luffy, Humiliated in the Great Mine!
Hlle auf Erden! Ruffys Demtigung in der groen Mine!
Ikijigoku: Luffy Kutsujoku no Dai Saikutsuba
L`enfer sous terre. Luffy et l`ignominie minire !

REGULAR.description:
On Gloom Island in the Grand Line, Perona finds out that her captain, Gecko Moria, is alive and she is about to leave Dracule Mihawk who let her stay there for the last two years. Meanwhile, Moria raids the Pirate Island of Fullalead with his zombie army to take back his friend from Blackbeard.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Das heilige Land in Aufruhr! Kaiser Blackbeards berhebliches Lachen!
Grabuge en Terre sainte. Barbe Noire n`a peur de rien !
Seichi Gekidou: Futeki ni Warau Yonkou Kurohige
The Holyland in Tumult! Emperor of the Sea Blackbeard Cackles!

REGULAR.description:
Dogstorm fights against Shutenmaru to ally with him for their operation but Shutenmaru still rejects their call. Meanwhile, Sanji and the others are on their mission to recruit like-minded people who become skeptical as they receive the secret message from the Kozuki Clan.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: En avant ! Un complot pour vincer Kaido !
Er setzt sich in Bewegung - Der groe Plan zum Sturz Kaidos!
It`s On! The Special Operation to Bring Down Kaido!
Ugokidasu: Datou Kaidou Dai Keikaku!

REGULAR.description:
In the Excavation Labor Camp, Luffy competes against Kid by hauling stones for food and they both get tons of it. However, Dobon, a vice warden, becomes furious when he finds out all their provisions are gone, and gives Luffy and Kid a new sentence: death.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Ooabare! Shuujin Luffy to Kid!
Rampage! The Prisoners: Luffy and Kid!
Remue-mnage. Les prisonniers, Luffy et Kid !
Riesenaufstand! Ruffy und Kid hinter Gittern!

REGULAR.description:
Sanjis Special Soba becomes very popular but some gang members come to disturb his business and knock over a customers bowl. Infuriated, Sanji takes them down and gives the customer, a little girl named Toko, another serving. Later, Sanji and his friends find out that Toko is an attendant to an important figure in the Land of Wano.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Great Sensation! Sanji`s Special Soba!
Dai Hyouban! Sanji no Ohako Soba!
Die Riesensensation! - Sanjis Spezial-Buchweizennudeln!
Un succs fou. Les nouilles spciales de Sanji !

REGULAR.description:
Wanos top courtesan Komurasaki is in procession and slowly makes her way to Orochi Palace. There is a crowd of people on the street as well as Sanji and the others. While everyone is fascinated by her, some seeking vengeance get in the Oirans way.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Eine Augenweide: Die Schnheit Wano-Lands  Komurasaki
Goukakenran: Wano Kuni Ichi no Bijo Komurasaki!
Luxe et splendeur. La courtisane de Wa, Komurasaki !
Luxurious and Gorgeous! Wano`s Most Beautiful Woman: Komurasaki!

REGULAR.description:
Zoro who has been wandering around the Land of Wano since he got separated from his friends meets a sycophant named Tonoyasu. Tonoyasu paid for Zoros sushi and to pay him back, Zoro gambles at dice. However, he realizes that the dealer and the others are cheating.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Tale of Chivalry! Zoro and Tonoyasu`s Little Trip!
Eine Geschichte ber Ritterlichkeit! - Zorro und Tonoyasu auf Reisen!
Ninkyou Den! Zoro to Tonoyasu Futari Tabi!
Roman de chevalerie. Les tribulations de Zoro et de Tonoyasu !

REGULAR.description:
Zoro is taken to the sycophant Tonoyasus poor hometown, Ebisu Town where people laugh away their misfortune. On the other hand, Wanos Shogun  Orochi has a lavish banquet while Big Mom is closing in on the country at a furious speed.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A State of Emergency! Big Mom Closes In!
Der Ausnahmezustand - Big Moms gewaltiger Anmarsch!
Kinkyuujidai: Big Mom Dai Sekkin!
tat d`urgence. Big Mom en approche !

REGULAR.description:
As the Big Mom Pirates approach the Land of Wano, Kaidos subordinates led by King and Queen try to get rid of them. Meanwhile, in the Flower Capital, another member of the Animal Kingdom Pirates, Page One, attacks every soba restaurant in the city, in search of Sanji.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Miyako Souzen! Sanji Nerau Arata na Shikaku
The Capitol in an Uproar! Another Assassin Targets Sanji!
Tumult in der Hauptstadt! - Ein neuer Attentter nimmt Sanji aufs Korn
Tumulte  la capitale. Un nouveau tueur menace Sanji !

REGULAR.description:
Sanji faces Page One, a Headliner of the Animal Kingdom Pirates, who questions the soba cooks true identity. Sanji uses Germas device for the first time and transforms himself into Stealth Black while dubbing himself Soba Mask.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Dai Katsuyaku! Seigi no Osoba Mask!
Dashing! The Righteous Soba Mask!
Die Heldentat! Der Buchweizen-Ranger der Gerechtigkeit!
Un fier guerrier. O-soba Mask, le justicier masqu !

REGULAR.description:
While the banquet grows livelier at Orochis Castle, Robin is confronted by his ninja force called Oniwabanshu. In the meanwhile in Kuri, Chopper, Tama, and Momonosuke train themselves preparing for the incoming battle but are interrupted when they find someone washed up on the beach.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Desperate Situation! Orochi`s Menacing Oniwabanshu!
Catastrophe. Les redoutables espions d`Orochi !
Eine verzweifelte Situation - Die bedrohlichen Orochi-Geheimagenten
Zettaizetsumei: Kyoui no Orochi Oniwaban Shuu

REGULAR.description:
At the banquet, the Shogun Orochi starts to talk about his late old enemy which bores the attendees. Suddenly, the Oirans child attendant Toko bursts with laughter and wont stop. Orochi becomes furious and attacks her, but an unexpected person stands in his way.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Das Bankett des Gemetzels - Die Riesenschlange des Zorns, Shogun Orochi
Pandemonium! The Monster Snake, Shogun Orochi!
Shuraba! Ikareru Daija: Shougun Orochi
Une scne de cauchemar. Orochi, le monstre  cailles !

REGULAR.description:
In order to save her child attendant Toko, the top Oiran Komurasaki stands up to the Shogun Orochi, but the yakuza boss Kyoshiro interrupts and does something that no one expected. Meanwhile, Robin is trying to get out of Orochis Castle with the help of Nami and Brook.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Die Blte fllt ab! Der letzte Moment der Schnheit von Wano-Land
Hana Chiru! Wano Kuni Ichi no Bijo no Saigo
The Flower Falls! The Final Moment of the Most Beautiful Woman in the Land of Wano!
Un ptale s`envole. La grande beaut de Wano s`teint !

REGULAR.description:
Nami, Robin, and the others got away from Odens Castle and now discuss what they have found out about the enemy so far. Meanwhile, Choppers group sets off to rescue Luffy from the Excavation Labor Camp where, at the same time, Luffy is in big trouble.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Das Band zwischen Gefangenen - Ruffy und Opa Hyo!
L`amiti derrire les barreaux. Luffy et le vieux Hyo !
Shuujin no Kizuna: Luffy to Hyou-jii!
The Bond Between Prisoners! Luffy and Old Man Hyo!

REGULAR.description:
At the Excavation Labor Camp in Udon, Luffy tries to save Old Man Hyo and stands up to Vice Warden Daifuku and Warden Babanuki with his physical strength weakened by the Sea Prism Stone cuffs. Then when a Lead Performer of the Animal Kingdom Pirates, Queen the Plague, comes to the camp, Luffy makes an escape!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Lead Performer! Queen the Plague Emerges!
All-Star! Queen, die Seuche, erscheint auf der Bhne!
Ookanban! Ekisai no Queen Arawaru!
Une superstar entre en scne. Queen la Pandmie !

REGULAR.description:
Luffy and Old Man Hyo try to climb up the wall and break out of the Excavation Labor Camp, but Queen the Plague stands in their way and gives them a hard time! Meanwhile, Nami and Robin experience a public bathhouse along with Shinobu and come to know about the Land of Wanos great yakuza boss.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Climb Up! Luffy`s Desperate Escape!
Klettere hinauf - Ruffys verzweifelter Fluchtversuch!
Yojinobore: Luffy Kesshi no Tousougeki!
l`assaut de la muraille. Luffy tente de s`chapper !

REGULAR.description:
Luffy fights quite a few Queens men at once in the deadly sumo match while protecting Old Man Hyo! Meanwhile, Nami, Robin, and Shinobu are cornered as Hawkins comes to raid the bathhouse. However, someone who they dont expect to be there pops up from nowhere to save them.
Source: Crunchyroll

titles.title: Dead or Alive! Queen`s Sumo Inferno!
La vie ou la mort. Le grand Sumo Inferno de Queen !
Sei ka Shi ka: Queen no Oosumou Inferno
Tot oder lebendig - Queens Sumo-Inferno

REGULAR.description:
Luffy deals with the endless supply of opponents trying to figure out the way to use Haki that Rayleigh taught him a while ago. Meanwhile, Zoro faces Gyukimaru who is accusing him of stealing Shusui, however, their duel is interrupted by a womans scream.
Source: Crunchyroll

titles.title: Gyukimaru! Zoro Fights a Duel on Bandit`s Bridge!
Gyukimaru! Zorros Kampf auf der Wegelagererbrcke
Gyukimaru. Zoro se bat sur le pont des brigands !
Gyuukimaru! Zoro Oihagi Bashi no Kettou

REGULAR.description:
The duel between Zoro and Gyukimaru is interrupted by Kamazo, Orochis assassin who came after a little girl Toko. Without Shusui, Zoro has a hard time fighting the two at the same time, but he finds an unlikely third sword to take down the enemies.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Big Turnover! The Three-Sword Style Overcomes Danger!
Dai Gyakuten! Shisen o Koeta Santou Ryuu!
Das Blatt wendet sich! Der Dreischwertstil berwindet die Todesschwelle!
Retournement de situation. Sauv par les trois sabres

REGULAR.description:
Luffys next enemies in the deadly sumo match in the Excavation Labor Camp are two tough Gifters. Much to Old Man Hyos surprise, Luffy keeps practicing using Haki properly at the same time as he fights them. Meanwhile, the wounded Zoro wakes up to find out the stunning identity of the mysterious woman he saved.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Zoro Kyougaku: Shougeki! Nazo no Bijo no Shoutai
Zoro est stupfait. La troublante rvlation de la beaut !
Zoro, Stunned! The Shocking Identity of the Mysterious Woman!
Zorro ist verblfft - Die schockierende Identitt der mysterisen Schnheit

REGULAR.description:
Hiyori tells Zoro a stunning story of escaping the incident 20 years ago and surviving until the present day. Meanwhile, Luffy stills struggles to master the Haki of the Color of Arms, but a surprising person steps up and gives an example.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Etoku Seyo: Wano Kuni no Haki Ryuuou!
Get the Hang of It! The Land of Wano`s Haki: Ryuo!
Meistere die Technik - Das Haki Wano-Lands, Ryuo!
Un coup  prendre. Le courant, le Fluide de Wano !

REGULAR.description:
Luffy continues training himself to use Haki with Old Man Hyos help, but the battle is suddenly suspended and shortly thereafter Raizo appears in front of them. Meanwhile, Nami, Usopp, and the others are wondering who Tonoyasu, Ebisu Towns hero, really is.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Tonoyasu! Der meistgeliebte Mensch in ganz Ebisu!
Tonoyasu! Ebisu Chouichi no Ninkimono!
Tonoyasu! Ebisu Town`s Most Loved!
Tonoyasu. La coqueluche dEbisu !

REGULAR.description:
Ushimitsu Kozo the great thief who robbed from the rich and gave to the poor gets caught and his true identity stuns Orochi and the others. When Toko hears the news, she gets very upset and so is Zoro when he hears the reason.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Hohe Wellen werden geschlagen - Die Identitt des edlen Diebes Kozo Ushimitsu
La rumeur se rpand. L`identit du voleur au grand cur !
Shaking the Nation! The Identity of Ushimitsu Kozo the Chivalrous Thief!
Shougeki Hashiru: Gizoku Ushimitsu Kozou no Shoutai

REGULAR.description:
Tonoyasu has been strung up and is soon-to-be executed. The people of the Land of Wano recognize who he really is and start raising their voice while the Straw Hats rush to save him. Then, Tonoyasu starts addressing the nation and the corrupt Shogun Orochi.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Der Sprint der Strohhte! Die Rettung des gefangenen Tonoyasus
Ichimi Hashiru! Sukue Toraware no Tonoyasu
L`quipage s`lance. Il faut sauver Tonoyasu !
The Straw Hats Run! Save the Captive Tonoyasu!

REGULAR.description:
By the time Kinemon and the others notice that Yasuie is trying to sacrifice his life to save their raid plan, it was all too late. Ebisu Town`s people laughing out loud annoys Zoro, but when Hiyori tells him the reason behind it, he is in for a shock!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: La colre de Zoro. La vrit sur les Smiles !
Zoro no Ikari: Smile no Shinjitsu!
Zoro`s Fury! The Truth About the Smile!
Zorros Zorn - Die Wahrheit ber SMILE!
!   SMILE!
SMILE!

REGULAR.description:
Hiyori and Shinobu tearfully tell the Straw Hats the truth behind Ebisu Town residents` cheerfulness and smiles, which infuriates them. When Yasuies daughter, Toko, runs to her fathers body, Orochi recognizes who she is and takes a shot at her!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Les larmes de Toko. Les balles cruelles d`Orochi !
Toko no Namida! Orochi Hijou no Juudan!
Toko`s Tears! Orochi`s Pitiless Bullets!
Tokos Trnen - Orochis erbarmungslose Kugeln

REGULAR.description:
Zoro and Sanji start fighting against Orochis clan. Nami and the rest of the Straw Hats join them. Meanwhile, at the Excavation Labor Camp, a new criminal, Hitokiri Kamazo, has arrived. And someone else who is brought to the site reveals the shocking truth about Kamazo.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Die Strohhte greifen ein - Tumult! Todeskampf auf dem Hinrichtungsplatz
Ichimi Rannyuu! Souzen! Shokeijou no Gekitou
L`quipage monte au crneau. Combat sur la place des supplices !
The Straw Hats Step In! An Uproarious Deadly Battle at the Execution Ground!

REGULAR.description:
Zoro keeps fighting Kyoshiro, but Orochis Oniwabanshu comes to back Kyoshiro up. Meanwhile, at the Excavation Labor Camp, Queen announces the restart of the Sumo Inferno with a new cruel rule which is painful not only to Luffy, but also to Drake and Killer.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: La rsolution de Luffy. Le Sumo Inferno doit prendre fin !
Luffy no Ketsui: Yabure Oozumou Inferno!
Luffy`s Determination! Win Through the Sumo Inferno!
Ruffys Entschlossenheit - Triumphiere beim Sumo-Inferno!

REGULAR.description:
Kinemon apologizes Ashura Doji AKA Shutenmaru for goading Holdem to attack Atamayama where Ashuras hideout was located, and asks him to join the fight against Kaido. Meanwhile, Chopper and his group finally arrived at the Excavation Labor Camp and Big Mom forces her way in to find her favorite soup!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Arashi Tourai! Ooabare Big Mom!
Der Sturm ist gekommen - Big Mom luft Amok
La tempte sabat. Big Mom fait un carnage !
The Storm Has Come! A Raging Big Mom!

REGULAR.description:
Craving red-bean soup, Big Mom attacks Queen, the Animal Kingdom Pirates Lead Performer who reins over Udon. However, when she finds out that the pot is empty, she turns her wrath against the one who ate it all: Luffy.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Grudge over Red-bean Soup! Luffy Gets into a Desperate Situation!
Der Sbohnensuppen-Groll - Ruffys Leben steht auf Messers Schneide
Les haricots de la colre. a sent le roussi pour Luffy !
Oshiruko no Urami: Luffy Zettaizetsumei

REGULAR.description:
After finding out that Luffy ate the whole pot ofthe red-bean soup that she was looking for, Big Mom becomes infuriated and goesafter him. Meanwhile, Queen, the Lead Performer, comes up with a plan to stopthe rampaging Big Mom.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Haltet die Kaiserin der Meere auf - Queens Geheimplan
Neutraliser l`Impratrice. La ruse de Queen !
Stop the Emperor of the Sea! Queen`s Secret Plan!
Yonkou o Tomero! Queen no Hisaku

REGULAR.description:
Queen hastily ties up the sleeping Big Mom and carries her to Onigashima leaving Udon to Babanuki. Babanuki uses a weapon that Queen made to threaten inmates and make them catch Luffy, but a mysterious figure emerges from the forbidden cell to save Luffy.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Brutal Ammunition! The Plague Rounds Aim at Luffy!
De funestes munitions. Luffy contre les balles excidmiques !
Die bizarrste Waffe - Ruffy im Visier der Seuchenkugeln
Saikyou Heiki! Luffy o Nerau Excite Dan

REGULAR.description:
Kawamatsu the Kappa is freed and stands up against Babanuki and his underlings! Listening to Old Man Hyos suggestion, Raizo and Kiku reveal their true identities which give the desperate prisoners not only a shock but also some hope.
Source: Crunchyroll

titles.title: Beginn des Gegenschlags! Ruffy und die Akazaya-Samurai!
Hangeki Kaishi! Luffy to Akazaya no Samurai!
La riposte. Luffy et les Neuf Fourreaux Rouges !
Start Fighting Back! Luffy and the Akazaya Samurai!

REGULAR.description:
Luffy faces those who are infected by the Plague Rounds and the non-infected prisoners who submit to the authority of Udon. To open their eyes, Luffy takes a measure that will risk his life. However, the Chief Warden Babanuki has something up his sleeve.
Source: Crunchyroll

titles.title: Kachi ni Kita! Luffy Kesshi no Sakebi
On est venu pour gagner. Le cri de guerre de Luffy
We`re Here to Win! Luffy`s Desperate Scream!
Wir sind hier, um zu siegen! Ruffys verzweifelter Aufschrei

REGULAR.description:
The freed prisoners in Udon refuse to fight alongside Luffy because he is a pirate. Raizo and Old Man Hyo try their best to convince them, but an unexpected person stands up to bring the prisoners hope after taking down Kaido!
Source: crunchyroll

SPECIAL.description:
After two years of training, the Straw Hats reunited at Sabaody Archipelago. Getting past the Fish-Man Island, they finally made it to the final sea  the New World. At Punk Hazard Island, they met Trafalgar Law again by accident who suggested them to form a pirate alliance with him in order to take down the Four Emperors, which they accepted, and together with Law, they went for Doflamingo who is connected to the Four Emperors. They entered Dressrosa, the country Doflamingo reigns over, and got into action according to Laws instruction but Luffy suddenly decided to enter a competition which prize was his late brother Aces Flare-Flare Fruit under the name Lucy, and made it to the final. Meanwhile, Law fell for Doflamingos trap and got captured. At the same time, the Straw Hats learned the darkness of the country from a toy soldier who they met on their way. Becoming furious about Doflamingos dirty trick, they joined the Little People to fight to take back freedom. Luffy was competing in the Colosseum but to rescue Law, he was trying to get out of there and thats when Sabo who he thought was dead, showed up

SPECIAL.description:
While Exploring the New World, Luffy and the members of the Straw Hats meets a mysterious girl named Olga. She is pretty on the outside but twisted and savage inside and she told them she is chased by the Navy and a powerful treasure hunter named Mad Treasure. The reason she is targeted is because she was from Alchemi, an island of steel which suddenly disappeared two centuries ago. Rumor has it that the metal called the Pure Gold that was created on the island is worth a fortune  that you can even buy the whole world with it. Thus, people have been seeking it from long ago. Olga managed to escape from Alchemi by accident but was caught by the Navy, and the Navy Headquarters and Mad Treasure who is working on orders from Guild Tesoro, the lord of the underground community, came to notice that there was a remaining survivor from Alchemi. Being pushed around by the cranky Olga, Luffy decides to hunt for the treasure that everybody wants. And the mysterious girl Olga is looking to make a lot of money using Luffy and the others. The members of the Straw Hats are excited about hunting the never-seen-before treasure. Will they be able to get the legendary treasure, Pure Gold, while having the formidable treasure hunter as their opponent?
Source: crunchyroll

SPECIAL.description:
The words that Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates, uttered just before his death excited the masses and the world has entered a Great Pirate Era! There is a group of young pirates who are about to set sail on the Grand Line. Monkey D. Luffy, a rubber man. Roronoa Zoro aka Pirate Hunter. Usopp, a sniper. Sanji, a seafaring cook. And Cat Burglar Nami. They, the Straw Hats, all place a foot upon a barrel and make their vows before their next journey across the great ocean. Luffy shouts In order to be the King of the Pirates!
A decade ago in the Windmill Village...
A little boy Luffy was enthralled with a pirate boss Red-Haired Shanks. But a group of mountain bandits shows up and makes fun of the pirates. Why didn`t you fight them?! Luffy yells out angrily but Shanks says that it`s nothing worth getting mad over. At that time, Luffy snatches the Gum-Gum Fruit from a treasure box and eats it and as a result, his entire body becomes rubber and he loses the ability to swim for the rest of his life!
A few days later, Luffy is surrounded by the mountain bandits again and Shanks comes to help. No matter what the reason, anyone who hurts my friends has to pay!!
Shanks and his pirate crew are incredibly strong and they beat down the mountain bandits. Higuma, the head of the mountain bandits, runs away kidnapping Luffy and heads for the sea. However, they encounter a local Sea Monster there and are attacked. Luffy is in a desperate situation... But again, Shanks saves the day. He outstares the Sea Monster and chases it away but in exchange, he loses his left arm...
When Shanks leaves the village, he leaves his straw hat with Luffy.
Come bring it back to me someday! Once you`ve become a great pirate!
10 years later, Luffy has grown up strong and he sets out for an adventure on a small boat. He again encounters the local Sea Monster for that fateful day. However, Luffy takes it down with a single blow of Gum-Gum Pistol. Luffys journey to become the King of the Pirates now begins!
Source: crunchyroll
